{"tid":518101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普︰我個核按鈕大啲勁啲","createTime":"2018-01-03T03:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-04T08:42:18.000Z","uid":28366,"like":65,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"74a447e90ee9b8beedba4524b2bf51f0ad9856d2","tid":518101,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:41:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/114103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F114103_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=f278761a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普周二在Twitter向北韓領袖金正恩「反擊」，指自己有一個比北韓「更大、更強」的核按鈕。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在帖文中稱：「北韓領袖金正恩剛提到『核按鈕一直在他桌上』。來自他那個被耗盡、鬧饑荒的國家的人，請告訴他我也有一個核按鈕，但那比他的按鈕更大、更強，而且我的按鈕是能用的！」<br />\n<br />\n金正恩周一發表元旦致辭時指，目前北韓的核武器已足以攻擊美國，「整個美國都在我們的核武器射程內，而核按鈕一直在我桌上，這是事實，不是威脅」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180103/57658724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57658724&d=2y2YLpLAH5IEjk2WPrbLkwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0e01f167\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180103%2F57658724&h=11324aba\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180103/57658724</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/114126_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F114126_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=95d1a720&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"889f6a257eb31dd4c874f65326d53cdacd319dda","tid":518101,"uid":28366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T03:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c001ba